<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Lower Mount Royal</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">Mount Royal homes are located in close proximity to medical services, from dental to
                family doctors.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located in Ward 8 of the Calgary City Council and Calgary-Currie provincial district, the
                area is currently represented by Alderman John Mar and MLA Christine Cusanelli respectively.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Mount Royal is home to a public elementary and junior high, with a high school on 17th
                Avenue.</p>
        </div>
